Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.90,0:00:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,?Shri Ekadasha Rudra Puja. Faggeto Lario, Como (Italy), 16 September 1984.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.52,0:01:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Today, we are doing a special type of puja which is performed in the glory of Ekadasha Rudra.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.75,0:01:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Rudra is the destructive power of Shiva, of the Spirit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.51,0:01:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now one power, which is His nature, is forgiveness.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.12,0:01:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He forgives, because we are human beings, we commit mistakes,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.81,0:01:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,we do wrong things, we get tempted,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.13,0:01:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,our attention is disturbed – so he forgives us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.94,0:01:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He also forgives us when we spoil our chastity, we do immoral things,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.69,0:01:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,we do thieving, and we do things that are against God, talk against Him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.95,0:01:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He also forgives our superficialities, jealousies, our lust, our anger.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.78,0:02:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Also He forgives our attachments, petty jealousies, vanities and also possessiveness.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.75,0:02:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He forgives our egoistical behaviour and also our subordination to wrong things.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.30,0:02:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But every action has a reaction, and when He forgives,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.24,0:02:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He thinks that He has given you a big grace-mark,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.19,0:02:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and that reaction builds up within Him as a wrath,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.25,0:02:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,against those who are forgiven,[who] try to do greater mistakes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.00,0:03:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Specially, after realisation,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.78,0:03:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,because such a big blessing there is of the realisation –  you’ve got the light and, in the light,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.28,0:03:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,if you are holding onto a snake then His wrath goes up because he sees how stupid you have been.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.24,0:03:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(Italian translator is confused so Mother re-iterates)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.33,0:03:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What I am saying is that after realisation, specially,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.63,0:03:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He is much more sensitive that,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.33,0:03:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,people who are forgiven and have been given such a big thing like Self-realisation,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.14,0:03:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,still they do wrong things then he is much more wrathful.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.79,0:03:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So, in the balance, the forgiveness starts reducing and the wrathfulness starts increasing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.11,0:03:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But when He forgives and, as a result of that forgiveness you feel the gratitude,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.65,0:04:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,then His blessings start flowing towards you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.21,0:04:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He gives you tremendous capacity to forgive others.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.42,0:04:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He pacifies your anger, He pacifies your lust, He pacifies your greed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.80,0:04:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Like beautiful dew drop His blessings come on our being and we become really beautiful flowers,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.98,0:04:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and we start shining in the sunshine of His blessings.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.99,0:04:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now He uses His wrath or His destructive power to destroy all that tries to trouble us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.94,0:04:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He protects realised souls at every point, in every way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.77,0:04:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Negative forces try to attack a sahaja yogi but they are all neutralised by His tremendous power of protection.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.76,0:05:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Through his vibratory awareness we are guided into right path.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.38,0:05:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,All the beautiful blessings of His are described in the Psalm 23 isn’t it, that’s the 23 Psalm ……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.98,0:05:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The Lord is my Shepherd” Is all described how he looks after you as a shepherd.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.39,0:05:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But He does not look after the evil people He destroys them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.61,0:05:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Those who enter into Sahaja Yoga [and] are still carrying on with their evil nature are destroyed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.62,0:05:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Those who come to Sahaja Yoga and do not meditate and do not rise He destroys,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.92,0:05:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,or they are thrown out of Sahaja Yoga.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.22,0:05:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Those who murmur against God and live in a way that is not behoving a sahaja yogi,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.48,0:05:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He removes them from [it].
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.28,0:05:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So by one force, He protects, by another force, He throws away.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.59,0:05:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But His destructive forces when they are built up too much,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.91,0:06:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,then we call it – now the Ekadasha Rudra is active.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.98,0:06:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now, this Ekadasha Rudra will be expressed when the Kalki itself will start acting,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.07,0:06:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,means the destructive power which will destroy all that is negative on this earth and save all that is positive.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.75,0:06:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So it is very necessary for sahaja yogis to expedite their ascent,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.62,0:06:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,not to be satisfied with the social life or married life or
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.46,0:06:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,with all the blessings that God has bestowed upon you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.10,0:06:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We always see, what God has done for us, how He has been miraculous to us,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.30,0:06:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,but we have to see what we have done to ourselves,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.76,0:06:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,what are we doing about our own ascent and growth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.37,0:06:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now the…out of the eleven centres…… Ekadasha, means eleven,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.48,0:07:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,the five come from the right side of your void, and five from the left side of your void.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.21,0:07:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The first five on the left hand side come from:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.79,0:07:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,if you have bowed yourself to wrong gurus, or if you have read wrong books,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.48,0:07:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,or if you have been in the company of wrong people,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.75,0:07:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,or if you have been sympathetic towards people who have been following wrong paths,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.11,0:07:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,or you have been yourself one of the agents or guru of these wrong people.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.29,0:07:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now these five problems can be solved, if we completely give up whatever wrong we have been doing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.72,0:07:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,As Mohammed Sahib has said that you have to beat the Shaitan, means the Satan, with shoes;
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.54,0:08:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,but that has to be done not mechanically but from your heart.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.33,0:08:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Like many people who come to Sahaja Yoga will tell me,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.50,0:08:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“My father is following this guru; that father is following that guru,”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.63,0:08:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and get involved with their father, mother, sister, this,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.13,0:08:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,that and try to take them out from those gurus, also get entangled.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.60,0:08:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Or some of them yield to others’ forces.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.57,0:08:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Like I know of Maureen, who was with me,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.10,0:08:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and her parents and parents-in-law said that the child must be baptised,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.26,0:08:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and I told her, you cannot get this child baptised because it’s a realised soul.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.48,0:08:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But she could not, that way, stand up to that,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.58,0:08:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and she took the child for baptism and the child became very funny – it was really like a mad child.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.43,0:09:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now then she gave up all that and so she has saved.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.77,0:09:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But supposing she had another child and she would have done the same thing,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.71,0:09:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,the second child would have been something very, very bad.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.17,0:09:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now, the trouble with sahaja yogis is that anybody who comes to Sahaja Yoga programme thinks he is a sahaja yogi – is not so.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.17,0:09:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Either you should have very strong sensitivity, or you should feel it in your body,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.54,0:09:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,or with your intelligence you should understand what is Sahaja Yoga.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.61,0:09:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A person who is still negative always gets attracted towards another one who is a very,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.19,0:09:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,very powerfully negative and does not understand that the other person is so powerfully negative, but gets impressed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.01,0:10:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Under such circumstances, such a person is hit by that negative person and Shiva cannot protect.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.77,0:10:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,One should not have sympathy with anyone who is negative, whether he is mad,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.59,0:10:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,whether there is something wrong with him, whether he is your relation, or anything.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.76,0:10:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No sympathy of any kind, on the contrary a kind of a anger should be there for that person,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.66,0:10:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,a kind of a detachment, angry detachment.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.84,0:10:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And this angry detachment is the only time when you have to be angry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.22,0:10:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But I have seen people who have anger for very good sahaja yogis
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.37,0:10:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,but not for their own husbands or wives who are extremely negative.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.92,0:10:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So when the Ekadasha Rudra starts acting on these five sides on the, we should say,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.93,0:10:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,on the right side it moves, because it comes from the left and moves to the right side,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.85,0:11:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,then a person starts becoming also negative but acting with his ego.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.29,0:11:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Such a person may take up a situation into hands and say that
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.94,0:11:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“I am such and such sahaja yogi and I am so, we should do like this and we should behave like this”,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.88,0:11:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and start dictating people. [They] can do anything.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.26,0:11:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And some mediocres or some half-baked sahaja yogis may try to understand [him],
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.67,0:11:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,but most of them will know that, “This fellow is going out, now he’s on his way out!”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.21,0:11:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So, all these things lead to this left side development, or we can call it on the head,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.18,0:11:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,on the right hand side of your medha, this plate, brain-plate is called as medha in Sanskrit language.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.82,0:12:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now, the right sided one, comes from the idea people have that, “I am myself a big guru.”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.99,0:12:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They start preaching about Sahaja Yoga also, as if they have become great gurus.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.60,0:12:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We have known some people who give big lectures in any programme
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.23,0:12:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and never allow my tape to be played or anything.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.25,0:12:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They think they have now become experts.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.65,0:12:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Then some of them say that now we have become so great that we need not do any footsoaking or anything,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.74,0:12:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,there’s no need to do meditation –  there are some like that also.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.52,0:12:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And then there are some who say that sin can never touch us,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.59,0:12:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,now we are sahaja yogis, we are very great evolved souls.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.87,0:12:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But the worst of all are those who just take my name saying that
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.64,0:12:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“Mother has said so and I am telling you because Mother has said” –
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.54,0:12:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,when I have never said such a thing, is all falsehood.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.84,0:13:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now there are some people who use Sahaja Yoga money and exploit Sahaja Yoga in such a way,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.70,0:13:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,exploit them, sahaja yogis also sometimes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.12,0:13:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And such people become very inauspicious.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.86,0:13:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Anyone who tries such things will go out of Sahaja Yoga with disgrace.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.33,0:13:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But one should never go near such a person,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.16,0:13:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,have nothing to do with such a person, have no sympathies.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.84,0:13:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Because this inauspiciousness will hurt anyone to any extent, so better keep out of such people.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.96,0:13:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,When these ten Ekadashas are developed within a person,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.37,0:13:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,then definitely such a person gets diseases like cancer and incurable horrible diseases.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.86,0:13:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Specially, when the eleventh one which is actually here,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.12,0:13:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,which is the Virata’s chakra, which is the collectivity –
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.77,0:14:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,when it is affected as well, then such a person cannot get out of this disease.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.25,0:14:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But these…out of these even five are combined, supposing, with Mooladhara or with Agnya,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.89,0:14:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,then they get into very serious type of dirty diseases.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.95,0:14:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That’s why, I always say that be careful about your Agnya chakra,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.29,0:14:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,because that is one of the worst things, that, once it starts getting combined with these Ekadashas,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.62,0:14:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,part of the Ekadashas, then anything can happen to a person,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.39,0:14:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,he can meet with a horrible accident, he can suddenly be hit by someone, could be murdered by someone,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.39,0:14:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,anything can happen to such a person who has got the right Agnya and also any one of the Ekadashas, right or left.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.76,0:14:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That means, the five of these, if they, any one of the five,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.42,0:15:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,if they combine with Agnya Chakra, the protective powers of God are minimum.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.76,0:15:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So, to keep your Agnya chakra alright, say now I am speaking, now you should watch Me constantly,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.31,0:15:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,so that there is thoughtless awareness and the Agnya chakra is soothed out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.28,0:15:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But, don’t pay attention here and there all the time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.48,0:15:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Then you will find that, gradually, your attention will neutralise into thoughtless awareness,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.32,0:15:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and your attention would be fixed in such a manner that you don’t have to worry about anything.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.31,0:16:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,In thoughtless awareness nobody can touch you, that’s your fortress.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.93,0:16:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,By meditation, one must establish thoughtless awareness, that is the sign that you are rising higher.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.33,0:16:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Many people do meditation and say, “Alright, Mother we are doing.”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.56,0:16:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mechanically, they do and say, “I did this, I did this, and I did this!”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.48,0:16:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But did you achieve your thoughtless awareness, minimum of minimum?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.60,0:16:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Have you felt your cool breeze coming out of your head?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.95,0:16:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Otherwise, if you are doing something mechanically, it is not going to help; help you or help anyone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.71,0:16:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So, after realisation, as you are very well protected,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.49,0:16:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,you have all the blessings and a great future,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.13,0:17:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,you also have a great possibility of a  complete annihilation.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.59,0:17:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I would say, to give an analogy, you are climbing, and everybody is supporting you to climb,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.36,0:17:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,holding your hand, and there are so many things by which you are protected,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.84,0:17:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,to be taken upward, there’s no possibility of falling off by mistake also,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.55,0:17:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,but if you try to remove your bondages with Truth and Love and
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.96,0:17:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,all the time try to hit the people who are trying to support you,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,then you fall from a great height, greater height.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.73,0:17:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I mean, the greater height you rise, the greater you fall, and with a greater force also, much more deeper.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.64,0:18:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But every effort is made by the Divine, every support is given to you, every care is taken – despite that,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.88,0:18:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,if you want to fall, then from that height, is very dangerous.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.53,0:18:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But Ekadasha Rudra, at that time, at such a time when somebody tries to harm the cause of Sahaja Yoga,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.64,0:18:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,after being in Sahaja Yoga, then hits you so badly that the whole attack is very widespread.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.63,0:18:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But the whole family can be protected if there are few people of that family doing Sahaja Yoga work; could be protected.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.60,0:18:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But in case the family that is against all the time of sahaja yogis and try to trouble them,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.72,0:18:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,can be completely destroyed, in a very bad way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.62,0:18:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now these Ekadasha Rudras come out of, as I told you, from the Void.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.13,0:18:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So, we can say that the destruction part of it comes from the Void mainly.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.42,0:19:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But these are the powers, all are given in one person that is the Mahavishnu, that is Lord Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.47,0:19:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Because He’s the support of the whole Universe,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.13,0:19:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He’s the personification of Omkara, he’s the Personification of vibrations.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.80,0:19:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So when He gets angry then the whole Universe starts breaking.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.35,0:19:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,As He personifies the power of the Mother which is penetrating into every atom,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.84,0:19:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,into every molecule, and to every human being, into every [thing] that is living and non-living:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.96,0:19:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,once it gets disturbed the whole thing gets into a jeopardy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.19,0:19:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So the pleasing of Christ is very important.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.54,0:19:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now Christ has said, “You have to be like small children”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.53,0:19:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That is, the innocence, the purity of the heart is the best way you can please Him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.88,0:19:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,As in the West, specially, people have developed their brains too much,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.17,0:20:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,they try to play about with words and think that nobody knows what they are doing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.55,0:20:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,All such people must know that everything you do is known to God.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.82,0:20:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If you are not clean in the heart, it is very dangerous for anybody to pose as if he’s a very good sahaja yogi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.99,0:20:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Such people are not possessed, nor they are conditioned, nor they are egoistical,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.91,0:20:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,but they are very cunning clever people and they are quite aware, as to what they are doing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.69,0:20:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But, there are people who get possessed also and then they, in that ,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.96,0:20:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,they try to destroy themselves or cry and weep and do all kinds of things.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.81,0:21:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There are some who think that if they hurt themselves
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.41,0:21:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,or do some sort of an extreme thing then God will be happy -are sadly mistaken.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.32,0:21:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If you cannot enjoy in Sahaja Yoga, then you should know that something is wrong with you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.68,0:21:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If you cannot feel happy in Sahaja Yoga then you must know that there’s something definitely wrong with you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.85,0:21:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If you cannot enjoy the company of sahaja yogis, then be sure something is wrong with you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.46,0:21:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If you cannot laugh and appreciate the greatness of God, then there’s something wrong with you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.96,0:21:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If you are still worried about negative people and their problems then know that there’s something wrong with you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.91,0:21:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If you have sympathies with negative people, then also there’s something wrong with you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.44,0:21:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But if you have anger for negative and all that is negative that is against Sahaja Yoga, then you are there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.49,0:22:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,When this thing gets matured then you become the power of Ekadasha Rudra yourself.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.85,0:22:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Anybody who will try to insult you or to do any harm, will collapse.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.55,0:22:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It has happened with many people who tried to be insulting to me or tried to harm me or anyway….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.44,0:22:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,sometimes I am quite worried about them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.17,0:22:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So one has to be in such a way that they become the Ekadasha.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.10,0:22:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nobody can touch such people.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.52,0:22:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But such a person is full of compassion and forgiveness.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.37,0:22:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,As a result, Ekadasha acts much faster.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.16,0:22:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The more compassionate you are the more powerful Ekadasha becomes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.39,0:23:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The more collective you become, the more Ekadasha acts.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.60,0:23:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Many people have a habit of receding back into their exclusion and saying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.34,0:23:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“Oh we better be at home and it’s alright,” but they don’t know what they are missing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.31,0:23:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Whatever may be your experience with others, you should stick-on together, always attend programmes,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.87,0:23:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,take leadership, go ahead with it, work it out and you will be blessed thousand- fold.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.53,0:23:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ekadasha Rudra are all the powers, I would say, of destruction, together.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.95,0:23:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Is the power, destructive power of Shri Ganesha.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.19,0:23:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It is the destructive power of Brahma, Vishnu, Mahesha.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.25,0:23:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It is the destructive power of the Mother.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.74,0:24:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Is the destructive power of the Ganesha…and four of these are Bhairava and Hanumana, Kartikeya and Ganesha.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.30,0:24:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Also the powers of Sadashiva and of the Adishakti.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:29.19,0:24:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,All the destructive powers of all the incarnations are Ekadashas.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.14,0:24:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now the last but not the least, is the destructive power of Hiranyagarbha which is the Collective Brahmadeva.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.95,0:24:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And this power when it acts, every atom explodes, the whole atomic energy goes into a destructive power.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.60,0:25:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So, thus, the complete total destructive power is Ekadasha Rudra.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.47,0:25:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It’s extremely powerful, explosive, but it’s not blind.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.90,0:25:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It’s very discriminative and extremely delicately woven.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.35,0:25:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It avoids all the good points and attacks the wrong things and it hits at the right time,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.47,0:25:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,at the right point, direct, without hitting anything that is good in between.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:35.31,0:25:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now the glance of Ekadasha Rudra falls upon someone, say, for example,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:40.87,0:25:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and there is something in between which is divine or which is a positive thing [then] it penetrates through positive,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:50.75,0:25:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,without harming the positive and hits the negative.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.26,0:26:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It cools down somebody and burns another.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:04.44,0:26:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Not freezing, it doesn’t freeze, it cools down. (Laughter.)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.42,0:26:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So that is how it works with such care and such delicacy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:08.22,0:26:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And it is tremendously sharp also.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.59,0:26:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And it’s very painful.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:13.56,0:26:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It’s not like cutting the neck in one shot, it goes on slowly, slowly.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:18.44,0:26:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,All the horrible tortures that you have learnt or heard about are expressions of Ekadasha only.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:28.63,0:26:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,For example, take the case of cancer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.58,0:26:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,In the cancer thing, you see, the nose is removed, the tongues are removed,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:38.83,0:26:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,then the gullet is removed, then everything goes on, one after [another], being removed with terrible pain, you see.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:48.80,0:26:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Take leprosy for example, the lepers cannot feel their fingers,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:53.51,0:26:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,they cannot feel it, so the…any rat or anything eats their fingers they can’t feel it,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:58.28,0:27:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,so they start losing their fingers, that is how Ekadasha eats up people, devours.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:08.33,0:27:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But this wrathfulness of the Father can be very gentle and could be very sweet, when it comes to His own children.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:23.55,0:27:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The story is about the Mother – once She got very angry, the Primordial Mother.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:31.39,0:27:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And She was so angry, She wanted to destroy the whole world with Her Ekadasha power and
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:36.20,0:27:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She tried to destroy the whole world.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:38.98,0:27:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,When She went into that mood, the Father Himself felt that She is being [a] bit too much angry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:46.81,0:27:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So when She started destroying, and She was going right and left,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:55.32,0:28:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He did not know what to do, so He took Her child, that means representing sahaja yogi, you can say,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:03.83,0:28:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,representing Christ or representing anyone of these great children of Her’s, that he put the child under Her feet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:14.64,0:28:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So, when She was stamping, suddenly She saw Her own child under Her feet and Her such a big tongue came out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:20.82,0:28:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She just stopped. Balancing. But this has happened only once. (laughter)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:31.39,0:28:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So, after the Ekadasha Rudra, ultimately the complete destruction comes through the anger of Sadashiva.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:42.59,0:28:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,When the final total destruction takes place.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:48.44,0:28:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So thus we have seen how Ekadasha Rudra acts and how sahaja yogis have to become themselves Ekadasha Rudra.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:59.85,0:29:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now to develop this power one has to develop a tremendous power of detachment,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:20.14,0:29:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,power of detachment, detachment from negative.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:23.47,0:29:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,For example, negativity can come from very near people,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:27.72,0:29:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,like brother, mother, sister, could come from friends, could come from relatives.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:33.75,0:29:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It could come from a country, it could come from your political ideas, economic ideas, anything like that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:41.60,0:29:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Any misidentification can destroy your power of Ekadasha Rudra.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:49.17,0:29:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So it is not only sufficient to say that “I am surrendered to Sahaja Yoga and I am a sahaja yogi,”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:53.95,0:29:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,but you must know mentally also what is Sahaja Yoga.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:59.17,0:30:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So that, intelligently, you understand what is Sahaja Yoga.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:04.12,0:30:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Because in the West specially people are over-intelligent
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:07.42,0:30:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and if the light of Sahaja Yoga does not enter into their intelligence you can never overcome your attachments.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:21.59,0:30:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That doesn’t mean you talk too much about Sahaja Yoga or you give lectures on that,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:26.66,0:30:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,but mentally you should also understand what is Sahaja Yoga.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:32.37,0:30:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Today is a special day when it has been asked that we should have Ekadasha Rudra puja,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:39.65,0:30:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and is for all kinds of false religious sects and false gurus and false religions,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:52.31,0:31:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,which are followed in the name of God, or any religion that does not say about Self-realisation
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:02.77,0:31:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and does not achieve Self-realisation and does not get connected with God, is false.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:11.89,0:31:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So any such thing that is just faith and talks of God but has no connection with God cannot be a true religion.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:23.13,0:31:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Of course, it gives a balance to people, but in giving that balance,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:29.40,0:31:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,if people live on that money and try to enjoy a wealth out of that money,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:43.10,0:31:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,then it is not even at the very lower level is the religion.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:50.19,0:31:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Like a balance, you, see, religion has to give you a balance to begin with, but in that balancing when they tell,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:56.29,0:32:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“You have to be balanced, but give me money for that, you must give me money, give me all your purse, give me everything,”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:04.05,0:32:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,then that cannot be balanced, it does not even have a slightest thing of the blessings of God.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:13.89,0:32:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Or any religion that makes you bow to anybody else but the incarnation, is no religion.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:20.38,0:32:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That’s another one which is absolutely false.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:23.54,0:32:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The real religion will give you a balance and will always talk about the ascent.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:30.48,0:32:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But they will not ask for money or make one man something great as venerated.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:36.95,0:32:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thus, we should learn to discriminate between falsehood, negative things and real things.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:47.95,0:32:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Once you develop that discrimination through vibratory awareness,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:51.85,0:32:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,or through your intelligence, you are in the control of yourself.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:59.49,0:33:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And then you become that power of Ekadasha, when you establish your maturity.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:07.54,0:33:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Today, I bless you all, that you all become the power of Ekadasha Rudra
